author: Raquel J.
text: Being a clinician & working in mental health for some years now I’ve seen & heard it ALL. It can be a very scary & dark place. And there’s so many factors that play into seeking & not seeking help/treatment. The highs & lows can be crippling, but there is hope.

author: Raquel J.
text: You can have all the money & fame in the world but that doesn’t “fix” or “change” your mental health condition. Mental health conditions are for life. However, there’s treatment for it. To help one cope & manage symptoms. My heart goes out to those who fight this battle daily.
